item.title: Paying for someone to help me fix Error_game_js5connect
item.dc:creator: @MrRspsMan MrRspsMan
item.description:

It just means that the server you’re trying to connect to isn’t up and working, if it’s your own source on your computer, try switching the IP address in the client to 127.0.0.1 or localhost then compile.
